<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA526_03_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema526_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema526_03_ih_0001">
      <section class="title group">
        <h2 lang="y"><span class="blue">[1~2]</span>아린이네 모둠이 한 달 동안 사용한 용돈을 나타낸 표입니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">한 달 동안 사용한 용돈의 평균을 구하려고 합니다. 안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page">
          <div class="tit_data">
            <div class="inner">
              <span lang="y">학생별 사용한 용돈</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="table_wrap row">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">이름</th>
                  <td lang="y">아린</td>
                  <td lang="y">선우</td>
                  <td lang="y">윤하</td>
                  <td lang="y">우빈</td>
                  <td lang="y">서진</td>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">사용한 용돈(원)</th>
                  <td>9000</td>
                  <td>12000</td>
                  <td>8000</td>
                  <td>7000</td>
                  <td>14000</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="inner" lang="y">
              한 달 동안 사용한 용돈은 모두 9000+12000+
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="8000"></math-field>
              </div>
              +
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="7000"></math-field>
              </div>
              +
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="14000"></math-field>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="50000"></math-field>
              </div>
              (원)입니다.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(한 달 동안 사용한 용돈의 평균)</p>
                  <p>=(9000+12000+8000+7000+14000)÷5</p>
                  <p>=50000÷5</p>
                  <p>=10000(원)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page">
          <div class="tit_data">
            <div class="inner">
              <span lang="y">학생별 사용한 용돈</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="table_wrap row">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">이름</th>
                  <td lang="y">아린</td>
                  <td lang="y">선우</td>
                  <td lang="y">윤하</td>
                  <td lang="y">우빈</td>
                  <td lang="y">서진</td>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">사용한 용돈(원)</th>
                  <td>9000</td>
                  <td>12000</td>
                  <td>8000</td>
                  <td>7000</td>
                  <td>14000</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="inner" lang="y">
              한 달 동안 사용한 용돈의 평균은
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="50000"></math-field>
              </div>
              ÷5=
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="10000"></math-field>
              </div>
              (원)입니다.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
